OL,3,CBP to cut 4,700 jobs worldwide as part
OL,4,Cof cost-saving drive
OL,6,FBP has announced it will be cutting
OL,7,F4,700 jobs globally, as well as 3,000
OL,8,Fcontractor roles, as part of a cost-
OL,9,Fsaving drive.
OL,11,FThe numbers amount to around 5% of
OL,12,FBP's 90,000 employees worldwide.
OL,14,FThe company has not disclosed how many
OL,15,Fjobs will be lost per country, but
OL,16,Fsaid the 6,000 petrol and service
OL,17,Fstation workers in the UK would not be
OL,18,Faffected. BP has 14,000 UK workers in
OL,19,Ftotal.
