OL,3,CBP to cut 4,700 jobs worldwide as part
OL,4,Cof cost-saving drive
OL,6,FThe London-based energy giant said the
OL,7,Fcuts were part of a multi-year plan to
OL,8,Fmake savings across the business, and
OL,9,Fadded there may be more reductions
OL,10,Fthis year and beyond.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIn an email to staff announcing the
OL,18,Fredundancies, Chief Executive Murray
OL,19,FAuchincloss claimed the job losses
OL,20,F"account for much of the anticipated
OL,21,Freduction this year".
