OL,3,CBP to cut 4,700 jobs worldwide as part
OL,4,Cof cost-saving drive
OL,6,FHe also said BP "had stopped or paused
OL,7,F30 projects since June 2024".
OL,9,FBP has also pulled back from a number
OL,10,Fof renewable energy projects, and
OL,11,Fabandoned a previous plan to cut oil
OL,12,Fand gas output by 40% by 2030,
OL,13,Faccording to reports.
OL,15,FLast year BP announced plans to make
OL,16,Fsavings of #1.6bn by the end of 2026.
OL,18,FThis was designed partly to
OL,19,Freinvigorate the company's flagging
OL,20,Fshare price, which has fallen about
OL,21,F20% since last spring.
