OL,3,CBP to cut 4,700 jobs worldwide as part
OL,4,Cof cost-saving drive
OL,6,FBP also announced annual profit of
OL,7,F#11bn last year, its second highest
OL,8,Fannual profit in a decade.
OL,10,FAddressing staff directly in the email
OL,11,FMr Auchincloss wrote: "I understand
OL,12,Fand recognise the uncertainty this
OL,13,Fbrings for everyone whose job may be
OL,14,Fat risk, and also the effect it can
OL,15,Fhave on colleagues and teams."
OL,17,F"We have a range of support available,
OL,18,Fand please continue to show care for
OL,19,Feach other, be considerate, and keep
OL,20,Fputting safety first - especially
OL,21,Fduring times of change."
